---
import Layout from "../layouts/index.astro";
import ModeToggle from "../components/mode-toggle";
---

<Layout>
  <div
    class="prose prose-slate dark:prose-invert prose-p:indent-4 prose-p:text-base sm:prose-p:text-lg md:prose-p:text-xl lg:prose-p:text-2xl xl:prose-p:text-xl mx-auto my-6 w-full max-w-prose px-6 text-justify font-extralight text-balance hyphens-manual sm:max-w-2xl sm:px-8 md:my-8 md:max-w-3xl lg:my-20 lg:max-w-4xl lg:px-6 xl:my-16 xl:max-w-4xl xl:px-4"
  >
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 tracking-[0.2em]">
      <h1
        class="text-left text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl xl:text-6xl"
      >
        Meet me, Yusoof Moh
      </h1>
    </div>
    <div
      class="mt-1 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-1 tracking-[0.2em] sm:my-2 sm:gap-2 md:my-3 md:gap-3 lg:my-4 lg:gap-4 xl:my-5 xl:gap-5"
    >
      <ModeToggle client:load />
    </div>
    <div data-mode="full" class="space-y-4">
      <p>
        In the name of Allah, and by His grace. My name is pronounced <i
          >yu-soof</i
        >, born and raised in Malang, now collaborating remotely across
        Indonesia. I am a <strong>full-stack/DevOps engineer</strong> running cost-efficient,
        self-hosted stacks with UU PDP guardrails. <strong>Web:</strong> TypeScript/React,
        Hono, Node/Bun; <strong>Infra:</strong> Docker, Traefik, Tailscale, GitHub
        Actions; <strong>Mobile:</strong> React Native, Capacitor; <strong
          >Observability:</strong
        > OpenTelemetry, Sentry. Recently, I <strong
          >accelerated time-to-production</strong
        > at Nadi—delivering faster, steadier releases—while engineering YDSF’s <strong
          >Muslim crowdfunding platform</strong
        > end-to-end: typed schemas and accounting records, web app, production APIs,
        and containerized deployments. I&rsquo;m also exploring pragmatic AI and
        &quot;boring enterprise&quot; SaaS for Indonesia. Beyond code, I cultivate
        edamame, enjoy regional motorcycle tours, and keep a steady habit of deep
        research. I base my understanding of Islam in accordance with the first three
        generations of the ummah, focusing on <strong>tawhid</strong> and <strong
          >tafsir</strong
        >. To further that commitment, I conduct <i>tahsin</i> classes and support
        local communities, aspiring to contribute&mdash;however small&mdash;to the
        da'wah.
        <span class="font-semibold"
          >Open to meaningful remote or contract collaborations.</span
        >
        You can reach out via
        <a
          class="not-prose cursor-pointer font-semibold hover:underline"
          href="mailto:me@yusoofsh.id"
          onclick="sa_event('email_clicked')"
          rel="noreferrer"
          target="_blank">Mail</a
        > /
        <a
          class="not-prose cursor-pointer font-semibold hover:underline"
          href="/twitter"
          onclick="sa_event('twitter_clicked')"
          rel="noreferrer"
          target="_blank">Twitter</a
        > /
        <a
          class="not-prose cursor-pointer font-semibold hover:underline"
          href="/linkedin"
          onclick="sa_event('linkedin_clicked')"
          rel="noreferrer"
          target="_blank">LinkedIn</a
        > /
        <a
          class="not-prose cursor-pointer font-semibold hover:underline"
          href="/github"
          onclick="sa_event('github_clicked')"
          rel="noreferrer"
          target="_blank">GitHub</a
        >. May Allah bless our endeavors, and lead us to His everlasting mercy.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div data-mode="tldr" class="space-y-4">
      <p>
        Bismillah. I’m a Malang-based, remote full-stack/DevOps engineer focused
        on cost-efficient self-hosted stacks with UU PDP guardrails. Recently I <strong
          >accelerated time-to-production</strong
        > at <strong>Nadi</strong> and delivered <strong
          >YDSF’s Muslim crowdfunding platform</strong
        > end-to-end. Open to meaningful remote/contract collaborations via
        <a
          class="not-prose cursor-pointer font-semibold hover:underline"
          href="mailto:me@yusoofsh.id"
          onclick="sa_event('email_clicked')"
          rel="noreferrer"
          target="_blank">Mail</a
        > /
        <a
          class="not-prose cursor-pointer font-semibold hover:underline"
          href="/twitter"
          onclick="sa_event('twitter_clicked')"
          rel="noreferrer"
          target="_blank">Twitter</a
        > /
        <a
          class="not-prose cursor-pointer font-semibold hover:underline"
          href="/linkedin"
          onclick="sa_event('linkedin_clicked')"
          rel="noreferrer"
          target="_blank">LinkedIn</a
        > /
        <a
          class="not-prose cursor-pointer font-semibold hover:underline"
          href="/github"
          onclick="sa_event('github_clicked')"
          rel="noreferrer"
          target="_blank">GitHub</a
        >. Baarakallahu fiik.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
